n chemistry recipes for readers to try out at home.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aConfidential communications -- History. 0aConfidential communicationsxHistory. 0aEspionage -- Equipment and supplies -- History. 0aEspionagexEquipment and suppliesxHistory. 0aInvisible inks -- History. 0aInvisible inksxHistory. 0aWriting, Invisible -- History. 0aWriting, InvisiblexHistory. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Intelligence & Espionage.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311067250340uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030018825740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300188257423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300188257/original  a978-3-11-067250-3  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles